og3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係黑警無紀律, 佢地拎住金牌, 亂拉無後果<br />\n無人制裁佢哋<br />\n係制度問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>所以更加要強調解散警隊 黑警死全家</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔用強權震壓, 佢地就會輸, 到時佢時就會輸得好徹底<br />\n佢地呢d 係垂死前掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832a70493101a81c922436abefb891856fe8f29b","tid":1800934,"uid":237627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"287b425c0e7d00c929c73f5b6b0eba1fed0736c1","tid":1800934,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"和你shop係無問題，我覺得唔洗著全黑，無視d狗，Window shopping<br />\n入店正飲水，入店&lsquo;長龍&rsquo;收銀位，開閃光燈影下藍店風景，得閒心情唔好鳩叫下，無人吹得你脹。<br />\n落閘就走，開閘就返，一家大細都玩得。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skMss7.jpg&h=077c238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新日程表出咗啦 除夕元旦都有行動呀<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1798785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1798785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"95a0c7134d1df6c22f5937b78b631f89d6404f06","tid":1800934,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"其實和你shop只係大家做演員扮傻仔在商場鳩嗌令到店舖停止運作姐"},{"pid":"c2864ada80e8a2dec9f79f97d229697fc782b77b","tid":1800934,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"突然思覺